open analyzer.pd with pd-extended:

http://puredata.info/downloads
or
git clone git://pure-data.git.sourceforge.net/gitroot/pure-data/pd-extended.git
or
In ubuntu, add: 
deb http://apt.puredata.info/releases lucid main
to /etc/apt/sources/


In linux, you can install aubio with aptitude install pd-aubio
and then you'll need to symlink the aubio package from /usr/lib/pd/extras to /usr/lib/pd-extended/extras
